headline: Here’s why some Ethereum traders expect ETH price to hit $16K this cycle
summary: Ethereum price is painting an ascending triangle pattern breakout with a price target of around $16,700.

headline: TON may become the first everyday blockchain by 2027
summary: TON, the blockchain natively integrated into Telegram’s 900 million-strong user base, is poised to become the first everyday blockchain by 2027, offering a user experience that makes Web3 feel like Web2.
